title: ANGRAU Recruitment 2025 - Walk- in interview for Young Professional -I Posts
description: The Acharya NG Ranga Agricultural University (ANGRAU) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Young Professional - I Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their Diploma can apply for the ANGRAU Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can attend the walk-in interview. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process...
